	    @Test
	    public void test() {
		    System.out.println(cachingConfig.getSpecs());
	     }

     }
And also you don&#39;t need `@TestPropertySource`, you can just use `@Profile` to load test profile and `@ActiveProfile` to make `test` as active profile for that test class

