    public &lt;R&gt; ObjStack&lt;R&gt; map(Function&lt;T, R&gt; mapping) {
        return ObjStack.of(mapping.apply((T) current), history());
    }
Where `T` is inherited from class signature `ObjStack&lt;T&gt;`

